Interface VesselDao.VesselProjection

Enclosing interface:
VesselDao
public static interface VesselDao.VesselProjection
Projection helper to support the conversion of result from native query object to a temporary Vessel entity Naming convention must follow exact name in the entity hence the lack of camel cased letters
